<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7600> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7600" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. and procos., Transalpine Gaul and Spain. His defeat should be dated between that of Domitius and Thorius Balbus in 79 (MRR 2.84) and the arrival of Pompey in 77 or 76. See MRR 2.83, 87, and Badian, Mel. Piganiol 910.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4296> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4296" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Proconsul in Transalpine Gaul (Caes. BG 3.20.1; Liv. Per. 90; Plut. Sert. 12.4; Oros. 5.23.4). Suffered defeats in Spain at the hands of Hirtuleius (see above), and again in Gaul (Caes.)." .
